local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["divagate"]={"divagate","['daɪvəgeɪt]","[ 'daivəɡeit ]","vi.(文章或谈话)离题",'vi.(文章或谈话)离题,漂泊','Please don\'t divagate from what we\'re discussing about! We don\'t need your political opinions.','请别从我们所讨论的事岔开话题，我们不需要你政治上的意见.','||Divagate|| is lose clarity or turn aside especially from the main subject of attention or course of argument in writing, thinking, or speaking','vi. (文章或谈话)离题, 漂泊'}
